assets.name: Bud's Braggy Selfie #9392
assets.description:
In Bud's vanity realm,
11,111 selfies at the helm.
Yet emptiness did creep,
Validation, a prize he couldn't keep.

Yearning depth, authenticity's grace,
Beyond self-centeredness, a new chase.
His gallery of pride lost its gleam,
Questioning worth, a shattered dream.

With clarity's light, he set forth,
Seeking meaning beyond self's worth.
Life's art, not just shallow facade,
Connection and reflection, paths to trod.

Selfies, relics of a bygone past,
Humbler journey found at last.
Bud's growth, a resurrection story,
No longer bound by numbers' glory.

assets.description:
Zerion DNA is a first of a kind Dynamic NFT Avatar ‚Äì a generative, living NFT that evolves over time to reflect your digital identity. Every wallet action renders unique attributes so that no two NFTs are alike. Wallet actions that will cause the NFT to evolve include buying and selling tokens, interacting with different networks and exploring the Zerion app.

To claim your DNA, create a Zerion Wallet via our Zerion iOS and Android apps.

asset_contract.name: Zerion DNA 1.0
asset_contract.description:
DNA is a new ‚Äòliving‚Äô NFT collection based on users‚Äô on-chain activity that is generated when users create a Zerion Wallet. This NFT will change over time according to the amount of gas you‚Äôve spent, the amount of assets you hold, the networks you support and more! DNA holders can set their NFTs as their wallet avatars and visually express their on-chain activity. Zerion‚Äôs mission is to connect 1 Billion people to Web3 and the DNA is about giving users a way to express themselves on-chain.

To claim your DNA, create a Zerion Wallet via our Zerion iOS and Android apps.

Other NFT collections from Zerion: [Zerion Genesis](https://opensea.io/collection/zerion-genesis-collection)

assets.description:
Cashmere is a cross-chain solution that provides a MEV protected cross-chain swaps and easy-to-use platform for people around the world to swap any asset between any chain.

To commemorate the launch of the testnet and expand the CashmereLabs community, we have introduced "CashmereLabs Testnet Early Adopter" .

We are enthusiastic about collaborating on the development of CashmereLabs.
